            "\x1b_Ga=T,d=A,f=24,s={},v={},t=s,S={},H={};\x1b\\",
            width, height, data_len, shm_name_str
        ).unwrap();

        handle.flush().unwrap();

        // --- 7. Prepare for cleanup ---
        // We store the FD and name to close/unlink in the next iteration.
        // We cannot close/unlink immediately because Kitty needs to open it.
        // Kitty opens the file descriptor passed to it via the escape code while processing the input.
        prev_shm = Some((shm_name, fd));

